<h4 class ="heading">What is HALAL Meat?</h4>
<div class = "dotted-options-border">
<p class ="text"> Halal Meat refers to the <i><b>islamic</b></i> form of animal slaughtering. It involves the cutting of the animals <b>jugular</b> vein, cartoid artery and windpipe. The reason for this is it ensures the least pain is being inflicted on the animal at the time of slaughter, as well as ensuring the quickest way of slaughter.</p>
</div>
